Map {
User Stories {
    Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view orders that are not supported by the Extreme Sports application.

Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select a travel time for my extreme sports activity.

View Activity Details: As a user, I want to be able to view details about the extreme sports activity I am interested in.

Book Activity: As a user, I want to be able to book an extreme sports activity.

View Booking History: As a user, I want to be able to view my booking history.

Cancel Booking: As a user, I want to be able to cancel a booking if I no longer wish to participate in the activity.

Payment Options: As a user, I want to be able to select from a variety of payment options when booking an extreme sports activity.

View Reviews: As a user, I want to be able to view reviews from other users about the extreme sports activities.

Leave a Review: As a user, I want to be able to leave a review about an extreme sports activity I have participated in.

}
}
